responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "AEA402CE42D603E77ECA618817C7E864", "Our Settler Militia and the few knights of the Kaealr Army I have available are already assaulting the bulk of the bovine brutes. I now await a band of Striders that are to infiltrate the ruins of Thanalas and seize the horn before the minotaurs do. However, the striders are long overdue and our window of opportunity is qucik to shut. Can you do this for the Kaelar Empire?")
